        "product_description": {
            "value": "GEAR AID Wetsuit Repair Kits make it easy to fix tears permanently in neoprene wetsuits, gloves, and waders. The heat-activated Tenacious Tape Neoprene Patch bonds with just a household iron, providing a durable, flexible repair that stands up to demanding conditions. The black, 10\"x6\" fabric patch can be cut to size to repair tears or reinforce high-wear areas like elbows and knees that require flexibility and durability. It is also compatible with stretch fabrics such as spandex and Lycra. This complete kit includes the Iron-On Neoprene Patch along with Aquaseal NEO Contact Cement (1.5 fl oz). Aquaseal NEO repairs torn or ripped neoprene permanently in as little as 30 minutes, curing to a black, flexible rubber that bonds to latex. Whether you're a diver, surfer, angler, or watersports enthusiast, this repair kit helps extend the life of your gear and keeps you in the water longer. Packaging may vary.",
